---
/**
 * Features — reframed from technical capabilities to school-oriented benefits.
 * The bento grid still sets visual rhythm (1 tall + 1 wide + 4 medium) but
 * each card now answers "apa yang sekolah dapat" alih-alih "fitur apa yang ada".
 */
---

<section id="fitur">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">★ Yang Anda Dapat</span>
      <h2>Manfaat Nyata untuk Sekolah Anda Sehari-hari</h2>
      <p>Tidak perlu paham teknologi. Yang penting, semua kebutuhan website sekolah Anda — dari berita harian hingga pendaftaran siswa baru — bisa dikelola sendiri tanpa drama.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bento">
      <!-- 1. Tampilan modern — TALL -->
      <article class="bento-card feature-tall reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect>
            <path d="M8 21h8"></path>
            <path d="M12 17v4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Tampil Profesional di Semua Perangkat</h3>
        <p>Calon siswa lihat website sekolah Anda dari HP — dan langsung yakin ini sekolah serius. Tampilan otomatis menyesuaikan: HP, tablet, laptop, semua kelihatan rapi.</p>
        <div class="feat-art">
          <div class="feat-devices">
            <div class="feat-laptop">
              <div class="bar full"></div>
              <div class="bar" style="width:40%"></div>
              <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:4px;margin-top:auto">
                <div class="bar" style="background:var(--surface);height:30px"></div>
                <div class="bar" style="background:var(--surface);height:30px"></div>
                <div class="bar" style="background:var(--surface);height:30px"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feat-phone">
              <div class="bar accent"></div>
              <div class="bar"></div>
              <div class="bar" style="width:40%"></div>
              <div class="bar" style="background:var(--surface-2);height:30px;border-radius:4px;margin-top:auto"></div>
              <div class="bar" style="background:var(--surface-2);height:30px;border-radius:4px"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 2. Update sendiri — WIDE -->
      <article class="bento-card feature-wide reveal">
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr 1fr;gap:24px;align-items:center;height:100%">
          <div>
            <div class="ico">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M14 3v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h4"></path>
                <path d="M17 21H7a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h7l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z"></path>
                <line x1="9" y1="13" x2="15" y2="13"></line>
                <line x1="9" y1="17" x2="13" y2="17"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 style="margin-top:14px">Posting Berita &amp; Pengumuman Sendiri</h3>
            <p>Mau update kegiatan lomba, libur sekolah, atau pengumuman PPDB? Cukup ketik di dashboard, klik publish — selesai. Mirip nulis di WhatsApp, tidak perlu panggil developer.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-editor">
            <div class="toolbar">
              <span>B</span><span>I</span><span>U</span><span>"</span><span style="margin-left:auto">📷</span>
            </div>
            <div class="line w-1"></div>
            <div class="line w-2"></div>
            <div class="line w-3"></div>
            <div class="line w-2"></div>
            <div class="line cursor"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 3. PPDB ready — MD -->
      <article class="bento-card feature-md reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M9 11l3 3 8-8"></path>
            <path d="M20 12v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Halaman PPDB Siap Pakai</h3>
        <p>Calon siswa bisa daftar online langsung dari website. Data masuk rapi, tidak perlu Google Form lagi. <em>(Tersedia di Paket Lengkap)</em></p>
        <div class="feat-art">
          <div class="feat-form">
            <div class="form-line"><span class="lbl"></span><span class="input"></span></div>
            <div class="form-line"><span class="lbl"></span><span class="input"></span></div>
            <div class="form-line"><span class="lbl"></span><span class="input short"></span></div>
            <div class="form-btn">Daftar Sekarang</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 4. Galeri — MD -->
      <article class="bento-card feature-md reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"></rect>
            <circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"></circle>
            <polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Galeri Foto Kegiatan</h3>
        <p>Upload foto study tour, lomba, atau wisuda — tampil otomatis di galeri sekolah dengan layout yang rapi tanpa setting macam-macam.</p>
        <div class="feat-art">
          <div class="feat-gallery">
            <div class="ph big"></div>
            <div class="ph"></div>
            <div class="ph"></div>
            <div class="ph"></div>
            <div class="ph"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 5. Akses bertingkat — MD -->
      <article class="bento-card feature-md reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Akses Bertingkat untuk Tim Sekolah</h3>
        <p>Kepsek bisa approve, TU bisa post berita, guru bisa kirim draft. Setiap orang punya kewenangan jelas — konten aman, tidak campur aduk.</p>
        <div class="feat-art">
          <div class="feat-roles">
            <div class="role"><span class="dot"></span> Kepala Sekolah <span class="badge">Approve semua</span></div>
            <div class="role"><span class="dot"></span> Staf TU <span class="badge">Posting</span></div>
            <div class="role"><span class="dot"></span> Guru / Wali Kelas <span class="badge">Kirim Draft</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 6. SEO — MD -->
      <article class="bento-card feature-md reveal">
        <div class="ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle>
            <path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Mudah Ditemukan di Google</h3>
        <p>Calon orang tua cari "SMA terbaik di kota Anda" — sekolah Anda muncul. Website sudah dioptimasi SEO sejak hari pertama, tanpa biaya tambahan.</p>
        <div class="feat-art">
          <div class="feat-search">
            <div class="serp-bar">
              <span class="g">G</span>
              <span class="q">sma terbaik jakarta</span>
            </div>
            <div class="serp-result">
              <div class="serp-title">SMA Negeri 1 Jakarta — Sekolah Unggulan...</div>
              <div class="serp-url">smanegeri1.sch.id</div>
              <div class="serp-snip">Akreditasi A · 5 jurusan unggulan · Pendaftaran PPDB 2026...</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <p class="bento-note reveal">
      💡 <strong>Butuh fitur khusus?</strong> Kalender akademik, e-rapor, integrasi WhatsApp — diskusikan saat konsultasi, kami evaluasi sesuai kebutuhan.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Visual mockups for the new "PPDB form" and "SERP search" cards.
     Kept scoped so they don't pollute global styles. */
  .feat-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 12px;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 10px;
    min-height: 130px;
  }
  .feat-form .form-line {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;
  }
  .feat-form .lbl {
    height: 5px; width: 30%;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: var(--text-3);
    opacity: .4;
  }
  .feat-form .input {
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .feat-form .input.short { width: 60%; }
  .feat-form .form-btn {
    margin-top: auto;
    align-self: flex-start;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .feat-search {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 12px;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 10px;
    min-height: 130px;
  }
  .feat-search .serp-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 7px 12px;
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .feat-search .serp-bar .g {
    width: 16px; height: 16px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4285F4, #EA4335);
    color: #fff;
    display: grid; place-items: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 9px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .feat-search .serp-bar .q {
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
  }
  .feat-search .serp-result {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
  }
  .feat-search .serp-title {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .feat-search .serp-url {
    color: var(--success);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
  }
  .feat-search .serp-snip {
    color: var(--text-3);
    font-size: 11px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .bento-card em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
</style>
